        <name>Temple by Ginger Moon</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6oz6Pf300mPPQvk-olDokJjNhPmkbpXiZV64l3_SrlTi1wS9YcX-ENIjan0UasdgPzTpy5pt_otkC5rY3con6CM0axC0u2Ruh2ePHwk38ibVbB_wTcm0o7nh12k-WEHovcet8qyq79s8jEdzJrPJlbRg-yDHhQ9OT9tzQtu5_veEKdY4jYAi4ZkkVMIj97_j01HrFLukf4ctJpIt-4WzLy5EwHZRHLmCT1HOWKGeiRxdCq50v6UZQIW2n45w?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>請看網誌的介紹&優惠項目：https://vocus.cc/article/657598bdfd8978000120fe20]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1577-E65100</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X6oz6Pf300mPPQvk-olDokJjNhPmkbpXiZV64l3_SrlTi1wS9YcX-ENIjan0UasdgPzTpy5pt_otkC5rY3con6CM0axC0u2Ruh2ePHwk38ibVbB_wTcm0o7nh12k-WEHovcet8qyq79s8jEdzJrPJlbRg-yDHhQ9OT9tzQtu5_veEKdY4jYAi4ZkkVMIj97_j01HrFLukf4ctJpIt-4WzLy5EwHZRHLmCT1HOWKGeiRxdCq50v6UZQIW2n45w?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
