      <Placemark>
        <name>峇里島庫塔喜來登度假飯店</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5hdap1VnclL8rYOj79Tfn-du0ri1bGPbTPNLX2MsDcErA_BY8mkOMYYFZiRTHc1MtR7Gr-LZR7U7rRP8VKKloixaU4Nj5YqE1UaAOD07TwE5fMNwsPQp8aGCmP8U6BoX2epVpzy_Xvc3jFisBo5fSQ3nJC_O-7lzQGDkGtIKpU5pDsevIHStkOu7mGdoD2VWVoURETw784BHVY_Q0wXEr2wLqPEtPHtYSW8R0mpZYVL7OUUw79bJ5JvRLE6g?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>詳細介紹請看：https://gobaligo.id/blog/kuta-beach-hotels/#sheraton-bali-kuta-resort-]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1602-0288D1</styleUrl>
